{"title":"GLUES \u0026 PRIMERS","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"christys-red-hot-blue-glue-half-pint-rh-rhbg-hp","title":"Christys - RH-RHBG-HP-36 - Red Hot Blue Glue (1\/2 Pint)","description":"\u003ch4\u003eRed Hot Blue Glue\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eContractor Preferred... \"The Original Blue Glue that quickly bonds PVC pipe \u0026amp; fittings for fast pressurization and maximum productivity\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe industrys highest quality \"Blue Glue - Premium formulation designed to bond in wet, dry and humid conditions\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIndustrys fastest acting solvent cement with the most active ingredients\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCan be used \u003cem\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ewithout a primer\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e for non-pressure systems up to 6\" and pressure systems below 4\", \u003cem\u003eif local codes permit\u003c\/em\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor PVC pipe and fitting applications; potable water, pressure, non-pressure, conduit, drain, duct, DWV and sewer\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ctable class=\"tbl_fixed_details\" style=\"width: 324px; height: 428px;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 113px;\"\u003eColor:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 205px;\"\u003eBlue\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 113px;\"\u003eMaximum Diameter:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 205px;\"\u003e6\" PVC Schedule 40 all classes and schedules.\u003cbr\u003e 4\" Schedule 80.\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 113px;\"\u003eBody:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 205px;\"\u003eMedium\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 113px;\"\u003eRelative Set Time:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 205px;\"\u003eVery Fast Set\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u0